This is my first E-Commerce Project .
There are five modules used in this project .

1:User Module :This module contain following API'S :
.Register  .Login  .Get Profile  .Forget Password  .Reset Password  .Get All User   Soft Delete User   . Permanently User Delete  

2:Category Module :This module cotain following API'S :
.Create Category   .Update Category   .Soft Delete Category  .Get All Categories 

3:Product Module :This module contain following API'S :
.Create Product   .Update Product   .Soft Delete Product   .Get All Product   
GetProduct By Slug 

4:Cart Module :This module contain following API'S :
.Add Cart    .Update Cart    .Remove Cart    .Get Cart  

5:Order Module :This module contain following API'S :
.Place Order   .Get My Order   .Order Cancel   .Get All Orders  .Status Update 




